Fig. 2A schematically shows a perspective view of the assembled cutting tool shown in Figs. 1A and 1B;
Fig. 2B schematically shows a side view of the assembled cutting tool shown in 2A;
Fig. 2C schematically shows an end view of the assembled cutting tool shown in Fig. 2A;
